### ========================================
### STEP 2: Read Articles
### ========================================

### Get all articles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles
Accept: application/json

###

### Get specific article by ID (replace 1 with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Check if article exists using HEAD
HEAD http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/1

###

### Try to get non-existent article (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/articles/999
Accept: application/json

